'''Hyperlapse'''是[[Instagram|Instagram]]在2014年8月26日发布的一款[[流動應用程式|移动应用程序]]，用于制作[[大范围移动延时|大范围移动延时]]和[[縮時攝影|缩时摄影]]视频。<ref name="forbes">{{Cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/amitchowdhry/2014/08/26/facebooks-instagram-launches-hyperlapse-ios-app-to-easily-make-time-lapse-videos/|script-title=en:Facebook's Instagram Launches 'Hyperlapse' iOS App To Easily Make Time Lapse Videos|accessdate=2014-08-28|publisher=Forbes|language=en|archive-date=2015-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151023134309/http://www.forbes.com/sites/amitchowdhry/2014/08/26/facebooks-instagram-launches-hyperlapse-ios-app-to-easily-make-time-lapse-videos/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="gizmodo">{{Cite web|url=http://gizmodo.com/instagram-hyperlapse-hands-on-video-simplified-and-sta-1626965309|script-title=en:Instagram Hyperlapse Hands On: Video Simplified and Stabilized|accessdate=2014-08-28|publisher=Gizmodo|language=en|archive-date=2014-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828041348/http://gizmodo.com/instagram-hyperlapse-hands-on-video-simplified-and-sta-1626965309|dead-url=no}}</ref>用户可以使用该应用一次录制最长45分钟的视频素材，并在录制完成后调整视频速度，以制造[[大范围移动延时|大范围移动延时]]的影片效果。<ref name="lightbox">{{Cite web|url=http://lightbox.time.com/2014/08/27/instagram-hyperlapse-timelapse-photography/|script-title=en:Instagram Wants Hyperlapse To Be ‘Another Way of Seeing’|accessdate=2014-08-28|publisher=Time Inc|language=en|archive-date=2014-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140830000226/http://lightbox.time.com/2014/08/27/instagram-hyperlapse-timelapse-photography/|dead-url=no}}</ref>延时视频通常通过拼接[[照相機|传统相机]]拍摄的静态图像制作而成，但这款应用采用的方法则是在原有视频上加工，并通过[[影像穩定器|成像稳定]]算法消除视频中的[[抖动|扰动]]，从而使视频画面显得稳定。<ref name="nbc">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/tech/social-media/instagram-launches-hyperlapse-app-shoot-smooth-time-lapse-videos-n189311|script-title=en:Instagram Launches 'Hyperlapse' App To Shoot Smooth Time-Lapse Videos|accessdate=2014-08-28|publisher=NBC|language=en|archive-date=2014-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140827220123/http://www.nbcnews.com/tech/social-media/instagram-launches-hyperlapse-app-shoot-smooth-time-lapse-videos-n189311|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="gadget">{{Cite web|url=http://www.engadget.com/2014/08/26/instagrams-hyperlapse-app-turns-shaky-video-into-smooth-time-la/|script-title=en:Instagram's Hyperlapse app turns shaky video into smooth time-lapse|accessdate=2014-08-28|publisher=AOL Inc|language=en|archive-date=2014-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140827035251/http://www.engadget.com/2014/08/26/instagrams-hyperlapse-app-turns-shaky-video-into-smooth-time-la/|dead-url=no}}</ref>与Instagram应用不同，这款应用不提供任何滤镜。用户可在后期处理时将视频回放速度调整为原始速度的1倍到40倍，这也是用户唯一可以调整的选项。

应用目前只提供[[iOS|iOS]]版本，但Instagram曾在2014年8月表示可能会在近期提供该应用的[[Android|Android]]版本。<ref name="wired">{{Cite web|url=http://www.wired.com/2014/08/hyperlapse-instagrams-new-app-is-like-a-15000-video-setup-in-your-hand/|script-title=en:Hyperlapse, Instagram’s New App, Is Like a $15,000 Video Setup in Your Hand|accessdate=2014-08-28|publisher=Condé Nast|language=en|archive-date=2014-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828044021/http://www.wired.com/2014/08/hyperlapse-instagrams-new-app-is-like-a-15000-video-setup-in-your-hand/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[打倒男孩|打倒男孩]]为歌曲《{{tsl|en|Centuries (song)|Centuries (歌曲)|Centuries}}》录制的[[MV|MV]]便是使用该应用拍摄。

